    "is_free": true,
    "description": "《Refight:The Last Warship》是由梵天游戏研发并发行的3D 战术竞技战舰生存TPS游戏，游戏采用UE4引擎打造了一个大型沙盒世界，为玩家打造真实的战舰战场环境。<br><br>在游戏中，玩家驾驶自己喜爱的战舰搜索资源、强化武装，应对敌人突如其来的攻击展开激战，击败对手生存下去取得最终胜利。<br><br><strong>巨型沙盒 自由探索</strong><br>在高达5200平方公里的广阔海域中自由探索，避过危险海域穿梭于群岛之间，搜集弹药物资强化战舰，随时出现的敌舰预示着危机的来临，激烈的炮战考验着舰长的技术与谋略。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007740/extras/f6557de85f0d86ba566a7ec6052ec202.poster.avif?t=1623229465\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007740/extras/f6557de85f0d86ba566a7ec6052ec202.webm?t=1623229465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007740/extras/f6557de85f0d86ba566a7ec6052ec202.mp4?t=1623229465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>绝境求生 胜者为王</strong><br>【战舰求生】30名玩家驾驶战舰在波澜壮阔的海域同场竞技，在绝境中获得最后胜利的舰长才能成为冠世军神  。<br>【强敌环伺】游戏中危机四伏，敌舰若隐若现，风暴圈逐步压缩着生存空间，轰炸圈侵蚀着安全海域，玩家的生存受到极大的威胁。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007740/extras/d038235356205b24e50b7811bc8e98eb.poster.avif?t=1623229465\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007740/extras/d038235356205b24e50b7811bc8e98eb.webm?t=1623229465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007740/extras/d038235356205b24e50b7811bc8e98eb.mp4?t=1623229465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>特色战舰 争霸海域</strong><br>【帝国亲王】各项属性均衡，火力续航优异、机动性能良好，高射速舰炮能够持续作战，混战游刃有余、舰队中坚力量。<br>【铁血宰相】拥有最强的装甲、最猛的炮火、最远的射程，一轮齐射即可重伤敌舰，既可前线交战、亦可后方支援。<br>【落日余晖】拥有最强的机动、最远的侦察距离，抢夺资源优势显著，操作得当可以规避远程炮火，隐秘的鱼雷能够瞬间击沉敌舰。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007740/extras/431b2968bb52b8cc3d6c89d62de3174c.poster.avif?t=1623229465\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007740/extras/431b2968bb52b8cc3d6c89d62de3174c.webm?t=1623229465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007740/extras/431b2968bb52b8cc3d6c89d62de3174c.mp4?t=1623229465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>装甲构造 内部核心</strong><br>【附加装甲】战舰各部位拥有不同的装甲值，根据入射角的差异可产生对应的等效厚度以判断击穿或跳弹，附加装甲会在被击穿时吸收部分伤害，亦有减少战舰着火时间。<br>【内部核心】战舰构造还原真实，击中核心区会造成大量伤害，弹药库被击毁将产生殉爆。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007740/extras/7835a52667cfa834eac029e98af8e75d.poster.avif?t=1623229465\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007740/extras/7835a52667cfa834eac029e98af8e75d.webm?t=1623229465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007740/extras/7835a52667cfa834eac029e98af8e75d.mp4?t=1623229465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>资源争夺 战术对决</strong><br>【武器装备】游戏中道具种类丰富，各型战舰拥有专属的舰炮、副炮、鱼雷发射管，提供截然不同的火力配置；提升战舰动力的引擎；提供战舰防御性能、防火性能的装甲；维修战舰故障的损管、提升战舰持续作战的补给。<br>【特色道具】潜藏于海中的水雷能够造成进水与起火、能够进行轰炸的战术支援、可大范围搜索敌舰的水听，展示着海战错综复杂的立体作战。<br>【战术炮术】鱼雷可作为常规武器，亦可作为封锁航道的战术武器；战舰交战距离较远，需要通过敌舰航向、航速计算落点进行炮击，炮术的差异直接影响战斗的胜负。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007740/extras/dc1f54471f4af56b7ef79b7cca4d7775.poster.avif?t=1623229465\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007740/extras/dc1f54471f4af56b7ef79b7cca4d7775.webm?t=1623229465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007740/extras/dc1f54471f4af56b7ef79b7cca4d7775.mp4?t=1623229465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>弹道涂装 彰显个性</strong><br>【炫酷弹道】远程炮火拖曳着炫丽的弹道，使无情的炮击成为鲜艳的礼花，切入弹道视角更可享受翱翔海面的欢乐。<br>【个性涂装】海面伪装色可使战舰与环境相融合难以被玩家发现、流光涂装能够显著的呈现玩家个性，同时也因太亮眼而容易被对手关注、琳琅满目的涂装种类总有一款适合你。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007740/extras/454f7f62b2582c05436bed996764359b.poster.avif?t=1623229465\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007740/extras/454f7f62b2582c05436bed996764359b.webm?t=1623229465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007740/extras/454f7f62b2582c05436bed996764359b.mp4?t=1623229465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>赛季挑战 玩法丰富</strong><br>【Battle Royale】独狼与小队均可体验刺激的Battle Royale模式，在强敌环伺的海域争夺物资、杀出重围，最终能够生存的一方将获得丰厚的奖励。<br>【团队竞技】30名玩家由10个小队组成，随机分配为两个阵营，双方将利用有限的物资进行交战，直至一方全部沉没为止，战术与技术将会影响胜利的天平。<br>【挑战奖励】每场对局均可获得战斗经验以提升等级，完成任务与特殊挑战将获得战阶点数以赢取丰富的战阶奖励，在战斗中的表现与胜负将会提升个人军衔以获得特殊奖励。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007740/extras/bdf9d4b8aec21955090a34de7a1a86d3.poster.avif?t=1623229465\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007740/extras/bdf9d4b8aec21955090a34de7a1a86d3.webm?t=1623229465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007740/extras/bdf9d4b8aec21955090a34de7a1a86d3.mp4?t=1623229465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
